    "reference_id": 19180,
    "title": "Lamentations 1:7",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25001007",
    "language": "eng",
    "content": "<p>laughed as she fell: See also <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer24:9\">Jer 24:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:5\">Ezek 22:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:4\">36:4</a>.</p>",
