    "reference_id": 19184,
    "title": "Lamentations 2:13",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25002013",
    "language": "eng",
    "content": "<p>Who can heal you? Reputed healers and prophets were all liars and frauds (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:13-Jer6:14\">Jer 6:13–14</a>).</p>",
