  {
    "content_id": 20054,
    "reference_id": 19222,
    "title": "Lamentations 4:21",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25004021",
    "language": "eng",
    "content": "<p>Uz was an area east of the Jordan River that extended south to Edom. It was Job’s home (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:1\">Job 1:1</a>).</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25004021",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:21",
          "end_ref": "25004021",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:21"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 20053,
    "reference_id": 19221,
    "title": "Lamentations 4:21–22",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25004021-25004022",
    "language": "eng",
    "content": "<p>The people of Edom were feeling secure and gloating over Jerusalem’s misfortune, but they, too, would experience punishment for their sins (see <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Obad1:1-Obad1:21\">Obad 1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer49:7-Jer49:22\">Jer 49:7–22</a>).</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25004021",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:21",
          "end_ref": "25004022",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:22"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 20055,
    "reference_id": 19223,
    "title": "Lamentations 4:22",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25004022",
    "language": "eng",
    "content": "<p>The first return from exile occurred in 538&nbsp;BC, after Cyrus of Persia defeated Babylon (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:22-2Chr36:23\">2&nbsp;Chr 36:22–23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra1:1-Ezra1:4\">Ezra 1:1–4</a>).</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25004022",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:22",
          "end_ref": "25004022",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:22"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 20060,
    "reference_id": 19228,
    "title": "Lamentations 5:1–22",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25005001-25005022",
    "language": "eng",
    "content": "<p>This chapter is a heartfelt prayer for restoration (cp. <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:4-Dan9:19\">Dan 9:4–19</a>).</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25005001",
