    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 20062,
    "reference_id": 19230,
    "title": "Lamentations 5:12–17",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25005012-25005017",
    "language": "eng",
    "content": "<p>These terrible things happened because the people had sinned (see <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa24:7-Isa24:12\">Isa 24:7–12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:24\">Jer 7:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer13:18\">13:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer25:10-Jer25:11\">25:10–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos8:10\">Amos 8:10</a>).</p>",
    "associations": {
