    "index_reference": "25005018",
    "language": "eng",
    "content": "<p>haunted by jackals: Cp. <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa13:22\">Isa 13:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa34:13\">34:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:11\">Jer 9:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:22\">10:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal1:3\">Mal 1:3</a>.</p>",
